      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty in person to believe it. I\u2019ve taken such incredible care of this car\u2014it\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition, inside and out. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make the next owner so happy. It drives like a dream and looks even better. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
