    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade FD3S RX-7, featuring the legendary 13B-REW rotary engine with its intricate sequential twin-turbocharger system fully intact and operating with factory precision. This chassis exhibits zero structural fatigue, maintaining its original 50/50 weight distribution and aluminum double-wishbone suspension geometry. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp 5-speed manual transmission and a Torsen limited-slip differential, delivering visceral feedback without the interference of aftermarket modifications. Compression tests yield optimal results across all rotor faces, and the complex vacuum line system remains in its pristine, factory-routed configuration. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a pinnacle of 90s JDM engineering in an unmolested, showroom state.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
