    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for 'mint' condition. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, appearing exactly as it did on the showroom floor. The exterior features a flawless, mirror-like finish with a professional ceramic coating\u2014zero stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any bolster wear or creasing, and it still retains that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the seat heaters, functions with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has been serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships, with a comprehensive binder of records documenting every oil change and inspection. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, showing no signs of fluid seepage or age. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a turn-key masterpiece that requires absolutely nothing but a new home.",
